 />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzm6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=2235e87b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=s5Gqkxkf8ApsCpMlSmcRzm6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=21f0cd75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會"},{"pid":"fe28f669ea2ea3a6e74a7111a13ea2f781a2c008","tid":1742700,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9dcc12cf22da75fe93c170a733a16ee53e7af53","tid":1742700,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:46:39.000Z","msg":"如果起外國，狗屋同狗宿一早燒灑。<br />\n得閒幫襯下狗屋同狗宿啦。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:47:38.000Z","msg":"而家狗宿重兵， 仲有休班狗自願做保安<br />\n<br />\n不過呢， 政府合署就好似冇人"},{"pid":"29b3468fa52316cd2b3f79d658eb8d80dc36788b","tid":1742700,"uid":316329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:18:01.000Z","msg":"左膠話警署係乜尻歷史古蹟唔搞得喎"},{"pid":"e782a55b4e4bc4cf8174ba5c5e554b9f29a7f8a5","tid":1742700,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9dcc12cf22da75fe93c170a733a16ee53e7af53","tid":1742700,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T01:46:39.000Z","msg":"如果起外國，狗屋同狗宿一早燒灑。<br />\n得閒幫襯下狗屋同狗宿啦。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:22:01.000Z","msg":"示威者已經好克制"}]}